item.title: About
item.description: FortyTwo Eleven is a Swedish-registered company through which koslib is offering consulting services. Clients are selected very carefully and we focus more on cultivating long-term relationships with good quality of product rather than maximizing volume. Some of the technologies we might can help with: Python Go AWS (containerized solutions) Kubernetes To get in touch, send an email at hej@42eleven.com.
